  <brief_title>Digital Breast Tomosynthesis in Younger Symptomatic Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>Digital Breast Tomosynthesis (DBT): Sensitivity for Cancer and Accuracy in Assessing Extent of Malignant Disease in Symptomatic Women Below 60 With Clinical or Ultrasound Signs Compatible With Malignancy</official_title>
